{"tid":678156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指協助朝鮮 傳美曾考慮制裁農行建行","createTime":"2018-05-25T23:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T00:20:06.000Z","uid":50457,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40a9880ebffa08031f50bc2dcb7f90700fbaf223","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T23:36:04.000Z","msg":"被指協助朝鮮 傳美曾考慮制裁農行建行<br />\n文章日期：2018年4月14日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】彭博社引述知情人士報道，美國官員對朝鮮去年夏季公開展示核科技和飛彈技術感到震驚。朝鮮此舉曾令美方考慮採取挑釁措施，以與朝鮮做生意為由，把中國第三及第四大銀行列入美國金融市場的黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士表示，該計劃很快就被擱置，主要是擔心懲罰如此大規模的銀行，會對全球金融體系造成衝擊。美國官員在分析經濟影響後，擔心可能引發系統損害，也憂慮中國採取報復措施。<br />\n<br />\n憂衝擊全球金融體系 計劃其後擱置<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，農行（1288）和建行（0939）暫時避過懲罰；又說美國不肯制裁兩家銀行，足以證明其對全球銀行體系的重要。<br />\n<br />\n報道指美國財政部最終改為制裁兩間規模較小的中國和拉脫維亞的銀行，資產均低於10億美元，並將它們列入黑名單；同時亦對被指與朝鮮有生意往來的貿易公司、貨櫃船及相關人士作出制裁。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述美國財政部發言人稱對事件不予置評。農行和建行也不予評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1523645722028&amp;issue=20180414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1523645722028%26issue%3D20180414&d=dLOC7UcvrPrvYfb6P9YwvWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=78e55f21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1523645722028%26issue%3D20180414&h=9c507616\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1523645722028&amp;issue=20180414</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然上個月新聞，但美朝如果開唔成會唔知會唔番兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且貿易戰仍然打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf9d347fcc4a5e52152de0146e32bc47b0954c9","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"美眾議員：中國農行及建行涉為北韓洗錢<br />\n05月25日(五) 20:02<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾院外交委員會亞太小組主席約霍周三（23日）表示，有證據顯示，中國農業銀行與建設銀行涉嫌為北韓洗錢。他又指，美方將會繼續跟蹤並對所有與朝交易或涉嫌為北韓洗錢的企業施壓，更考慮對相關企業採取「第三方制裁」。 <br />\n<br />\n約霍在訪問中表示，北韓領袖金正恩是否希望坐到談判桌前，需由他本人決定。而總統特朗普雖然曾談及打造「富裕的北韓」，但開始討論相關代價仍然為時尚早。約霍又補充，眾議院外交委員會正討論對與朝相關企業進行追加制裁的方案。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/mobile/bknint-20180525200237625-0525_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180525%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180525200237625-0525_17011_001.html&d=dLOC7UcvrPrvYfb6P9YwvWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3fc06245\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/mobile/bknint-20180525200237625-0525_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6025cc014106c55f99f0f9bb25137eb4993a9054","tid":678156,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣國侵實放生中国大行啦"},{"pid":"f07c56ae67674c7b26ada6f033aaad337af1c7cc","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"尋晚的新聞，好可能下一批制裁對象<br />\n<br />\n內銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635f8a54b8ebc310950e20110b82c4bfac7ed082","tid":678156,"uid":87745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"咁大間通常都係罰錢了事<br />\n好似hsbc咁"},{"pid":"9680dd07bffb86d7f294f4ccc030d953870a4d85","tid":678156,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"仲考慮咋 渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da730206f1bbe6f100122c9ad74872a564e280b4","tid":678156,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"怕你麼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715ea1c115b6e476b7e0fb32b211f58c444fa78b","tid":678156,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"聽日不問價沽哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf113eaf16ceee2d095fbbd0d2bf42c1f07ccd9e","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貿易戰開蘿，內銀一定會係BOSS級<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f45ea037d02deece1566caf4065d218c1c3fb0","tid":678156,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf113eaf16ceee2d095fbbd0d2bf42c1f07ccd9e","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貿易戰開蘿，內銀一定會係BOSS級<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:26:12.000Z","msg":"咁香港係咩級？"},{"pid":"1ff81b2c124a01d3192a8499de8f31143b5d6609","tid":678156,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:31:29.000Z","msg":"之前同北韓鬧交，就應該乘機制裁內銀<br />\n<br />\n而家關係好似好左，冇咁容易制裁<br />\n<br />\n如果金仔見完棋王，有咩反美舉動，就馬上恢復軍演，順手制裁內銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b8b2846ceaae900fbee8ac6211b72fb018bd9e","tid":678156,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:20:06.000Z","msg":"華為同內銀，其中一樣可能係下一波貿易戰中心"}]}